Get started

  1. Copy the entire /webfonts folder and the css into your projectâ€™s static assets directory.
  2. Add the following line into the <head> of each template or page that you want to use Uicons on.

    <link href="/your-path-to-uicons/css/uicons-solid-straight.css" rel="stylesheet">
  3. Use the icons with the tags <i> or <span>.

    <i class="fi fi-ss-camera">
<span class="fi fi-ss-camera">
